div(class="relative min-h-full overflow-hidden bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center", style="background-image: url('/assets/bg-login.optimized.webp')")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/60")

    div(class="relative mx-auto flex min-h-screen max-w-6xl items-center px-5 py-8")
        div(class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_440px] lg:items-center")
            section(class="hidden min-h-[520px] flex-col justify-between text-white lg:flex")
                div
                    div(class="flex items-center gap-3")
                        div(*ngIf="!hasLogo()", class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white text-sm font-black text-zinc-950") DI
                        div(*ngIf="hasLogo()", class="flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-white")
                            img([src]="appearance.logo_url", [alt]="title()", class="h-full w-full object-contain")
                        div
                            p(class="text-base font-semibold") {{title()}}
                            p(class="text-sm text-zinc-300") 운영 콘솔
                    div(class="mt-12 max-w-xl")
                        h1(class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight") 서비스 운영을 한 곳에서 관리합니다.
                        p(class="mt-4 max-w-lg text-base leading-7 text-zinc-200") 서버, 서비스, 도메인 연결 상태를 확인하고 필요한 조치를 바로 실행할 수 있습니다.
                div(class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-3 py-3 backdrop-blur")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-server text-sm text-sky-200")
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold") 서버 관리
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-3 py-3 backdrop-blur")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-layer-group text-sm text-emerald-200")
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold") 서비스 운영
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-white/15 bg-white/10 px-3 py-3 backdrop-blur")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-sm text-amber-200")
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold") 접속 보호

            section(class="rounded-md border border-white/20 bg-white/95 p-5 shadow-xl backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95 md:p-6")
                div(class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3 lg:hidden")
                    div(*ngIf="!hasLogo()", class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-zinc-950 text-sm font-black text-white dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950") DI
                    div(*ngIf="hasLogo()", class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-white")
                        img([src]="appearance.logo_url", [alt]="title()", class="h-full w-full object-contain")
                    div
                        p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{title()}}
                        p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 운영 콘솔

                div(*ngIf="loading()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.

                div(*ngIf="!loading() && requiresSetup()", class="max-h-[calc(100vh-7rem)] space-y-5 overflow-y-auto pr-1")
                    div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4")
                        div
                            h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 초기 설정
                            p(class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 운영자 비밀번호와 기본 서버 정보를 설정합니다.
                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-amber-700 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-300") 설정 필요

                    div(class="rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-sky-900 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/30 dark:text-sky-200")
                        div(class="flex items-start gap-3")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mt-0.5 text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-300")
                            div
                                p(class="font-semibold") 기본 환경을 확인했습니다.
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-sky-800 dark:text-sky-300") 특별한 구성이 아니면 비밀번호만 정하고 설정을 완료하세요.

                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-2")
                        label(class="block")
                            span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 관리자 비밀번호
                            input(type="password", autocomplete="new-password", data-testid="setup-password-input", [(ngModel)]="data.setup.password", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                        label(class="block")
                            span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 비밀번호 확인
                            input(type="password", autocomplete="new-password", data-testid="setup-confirm-password-input", [(ngModel)]="data.setup.confirm_password", (keyup.enter)="completeSetup()", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                    div(class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2")
                        div(*ngFor="let check of setupChecks()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-2 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{check.label}}
                            p(class="mt-1 truncate text-sm font-semibold", [ngClass]="check.ok ? 'text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-300' : 'text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300'") {{check.value}}

                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between")
                            div
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 서비스 백업 저장소
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="data.setup.backup_system.enabled ? 'border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 text-sky-700 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/40 dark:text-sky-300' : 'border-zinc-200 bg-white text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-400'") {{backupStatusLabel()}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 이미지를 보관해 필요할 때 이전 상태로 되돌릴 수 있습니다.
                            label(class="inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200")
                                input(type="checkbox", [(ngModel)]="data.setup.backup_system.enabled", class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-zinc-300 text-zinc-900 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                span 사용
                        div(class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2")
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white px-3 py-2 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 저장 경로
                                p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100", [title]="data.setup.backup_system.data_path") {{data.setup.backup_system.data_path || backupStatus().data_path || '-'}}
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white px-3 py-2 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 여유 공간
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100") {{backupStorageText()}}

                    button(type="button", (click)="toggleAdvancedSetup()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="advancedSetup() ? 'fa-chevron-up' : 'fa-chevron-down'")
                        span 고급 설정 {{advancedSetup() ? '닫기' : '열기'}}

                    div(*ngIf="advancedSetup()", class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 md:grid-cols-2")
                        label(class="block")
                            span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서버 대표 IP
                            input(type="text", data-testid="setup-advertise-address", [(ngModel)]="data.setup.advertise_address", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                        label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                            span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 파일 저장 경로
                            input(type="text", data-testid="setup-template-root", [(ngModel)]="data.setup.template_root", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                    button(type="button", data-testid="setup-submit", (click)="completeSetup()", class="inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-check")
                        span 설정 완료

                div(*ngIf="!loading() && !requiresSetup()", class="space-y-5")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 운영자 접속
                        p(class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 관리자 비밀번호를 입력하세요.

                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 비밀번호
                        input(type="password", autocomplete="current-password", aria-label="비밀번호", data-testid="password-input", [(ngModel)]="data.password", (keyup.enter)="login()", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                    button(type="button", data-testid="login-submit", (click)="login()", class="inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-to-bracket")
                        span 접속
